# HexStrike Execution Protocol

**Запрещено** выполнять forensic/recon/ops задачи напрямую (standalone Python, curl RPC, ad-hoc eth_getLogs).

**Обязательный путь:**

```
Mac:  python3 hexstrike_orchestrator.py <command>
VPS:  ssh hexstrike-vps → /opt/hexstrike-ai → legacy pipeline
```

## Mac — orchestrator (entry point)

| Задача | Команда |
|--------|---------|
| Статус | `python3 hexstrike_orchestrator.py status` |
| Forensics analyze | `python3 hexstrike_orchestrator.py analyze <0x...>` |
| Rhino bridge P2 | `python3 hexstrike_orchestrator.py bridge-decode` |
| RPC recon | `python3 hexstrike_orchestrator.py recon` |
| Infra trace | `python3 hexstrike_orchestrator.py trace-infra --target-ip <ip>` |
| RAG search | `rag-env/bin/python scripts/rag_core.py --search "..."` |

## VPS — remote agents

```bash
ssh hexstrike-vps
cd /opt/hexstrike-ai && ./scripts/vps-status.sh
cd /opt/hexstrike-ai && ./hexstrike-orchestrator run-all   # legacy pipeline
```

Host: `78.27.235.70` · alias: `hexstrike-vps` · install: `/opt/hexstrike-ai`

## MCP / agents (через orchestrator, не вручную)

- `mcp_rpc_gateway` — RPC (lab: `config/rpc_config.json`)
